    "\n",
    "Fetch and display upcoming NRL matches for the weekend with ML predictions.\n",
    "\n",
    "## Features:\n",
    "- Fetch upcoming fixtures from NRL website\n",
    "- Display match previews\n",
    "- ML predictions for each match\n",
    "- Betting insights"
   ]
